{
  "stem": "23645.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they made a sling for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took me out in the, in the field there and showed me how to use this sling.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was pretty good at it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And anybody that approached me, you know, I just put my weapon in front of me, and, and-- For the longest time after this, you know, my brothers would shadow me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would just follow me and make sure that no harm came to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That, that was the only incident.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it sort of wisened me up, and I had to be on my guard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a very costly lesson to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because it sort of shattered my, my thinking and my relationship with these two, for instance-- this brother and sister, which I, I held kind of dearly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was a bit disillusioned, not  'a bit,' but a lot disillusioned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- but it brought my Jewishness home to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I realized that we were different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I did, but guardedly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, you know, I didn't let my guard down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was always on the lookout.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You want to be a friend-- friends?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was more or less on my terms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was a shame, because, before that, I gave it all, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After that, when they invited me over, I never slept over, after that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My trust had disappeared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From what I found out-- I looked it up at Yad Vashem-- and what I remember reading about it, I think there were some-- almost about 4,000 Jewish people in Skarzysko.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the proportion of that with large families, of course, there were some 1,400 or 1,500 children, you know, under-- under the age of 15.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think the percentage of the ones that survived are minute.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
